title: Personalized Cat Collar with Engraved Name and Phone Number - Customizable Kitten Collars for Boys and Girls (Velvet)
features: Non-breakaway collar designed for indoor cats, providing security and durability
Comfortable and lightweight design ensures your cat hardly notices they are wearing it
Engraved name and phone number are clear and easy to read, providing added safety
The metal clasp is simple to open and close for quick adjustments
Removable cute bell with pleasant sound adds a touch of style to your cat's collar
description: Soft and comfortable: Many people appreciate how soft and gentle the collars are on their cat's skin, without causing any irritation. Durable and sturdy: Collars that are sturdy and long-lasting are important to keep your cat safe and secure. Customizable: Being able to personalize the collar with your cat's name and your contact information is important in case they get lost. No dangling tags: Collars with the information printed on the clasp or buckle are preferred by many because there are no dangling tags that can get caught or snagged. Secure clasp: Many cat owners prefer collars that don't have a breakaway buckle, especially if their cat is an indoor cat or not very active. A secure clasp ensures the collar stays on and doesn't easily come off. Quiet bell: A bell that is not too loud and annoying is preferred by many, especially if the cat wears the collar all the time. Cute design: Many cat owners appreciate the cute and stylish designs available, including velvet and bowtie options.
